title: Divine Detours | Joel Osteen
itunes:title: Divine Detours | Joel Osteen
description:
Sometimes what looks like a setback is really a divine detour. God can use the delays and disappointments to get you to your purpose. 

Your best days are still ahead, and together we can make a difference in this world with the message of God's hope and love.

To give visit JoelOsteen.com/GiveHope
